name: Queen Amidala, Ruler Of Naboo
Lore: 'Naboo leader. Frustrated by the Trade Federation''s control of her planet, Amidala came to the Senate to plead her case in person.',
Text: 'Agendas: justice, peace. While in a senate majority, once during your control phase, may retrieve 1 Force for each Naboo site you control. May be placed on your Political Effect instead of a senator. Immune to attrition < 3.',
